## Usage

```bash
# Check system pulse
bin/sys-check-pulse

# Generate a deterministic UID
bin/sys-uid ent "genesis-payload-string"

# Log an event to the ledger
bin/sys-log-event --type ENTITY_CREATED --targets ent_XXXXX

# Register a heartbeat locus
bin/sys-heartbeat --uid ent_XXXXX --locus-type formal --uri "path/to/file"

# Enrich frontmatter from atom registry
bin/sys-enrich-frontmatter
```

